This paper is about video saliency detection using deep learning techniques, which is a topic related to computer vision (cs.CV). The proposed method involves the use of both bottom-up and top-down strategies, which suggests the involvement of artificial intelligence (cs.AI) techniques. The paper also discusses the selection and ranking of salient features, which is a topic related to machine learning (cs.LG). Additionally, the paper evaluates the proposed method on benchmark datasets, which is a topic related to multimedia (cs.MM) and information retrieval (cs.IR).
